parameters.name: BR
parameters.description:
Magnetic field radial component in RTN       
                                 coordinates <nT>.

parameters.name: BT
parameters.description:
Magnetic field tangential component in RTN   
                                 coordinates <nT>.

parameters.name: BN
parameters.description:
Magnetic field normal component in RTN       
                                 coordinates <nT>.

parameters.name: R
parameters.description:
Distance of the spacecraft from the Sun      
                                 <AU>.

parameters.name: AVG_CON
parameters.description:
Sample rate (decimation rate) of recursively 
                                 filtered data.

parameters.name: LAMBDA
parameters.description:
Magnetic longtitude caluculated using        
                                 lambda=atan2(Bt, Br)
